{"tid":23920,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"做過X丸水產，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T09:58:50.000Z","uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b0bde6f64ec033987ad26adfe4651eaa7fdaa9","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"總店係尖沙咀，最近係銅鑼灣開分店<br />\n利申 我之前係做尖沙咀果間，做過一排，成間店都好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (衛生，管理等等)<br />\n歡迎提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c8982117ddd9eb029a6e2d4a89feda008209ee","tid":23920,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"有咩問題你直接講出嚟先啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b247a36afee5e634c134d49aaf5ec813e6e7eafd","tid":23920,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？"},{"pid":"bf822c8ca72603a4e0398da02d69c27777374a83","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩問題你直接講出嚟先啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大量曱甴同有老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過老鼠係個場行黎行去，啲客見到就反映，點知經理事後將件事怪我地前線人員，平時包飯結果果幾日都無飯食，但到我走果日都無處理過老鼠，得閒就見到佢係天花走黎走去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bbfc45262ceba459e2b3cf530740bda85c8c95","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用"},{"pid":"8f904003d8e6cd12f5d6e5a30f4d7cd74ce68ebc","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 刺身個帶子係急凍貨黎 個刺身帶子殻keep住回收再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc917a050701428c195f23fbd97aa2f8d3580116","tid":23920,"uid":45354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 刺身個帶子係急凍貨黎 個刺身帶子殻keep住回收再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁叫咩食會比較安全？<br />\n<br />\n利申：食過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95846b3fc1929e37b9e43e19c4acf906eb81f23b","tid":23920,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9c4f2391853d96a03d6f7ae96c5d6eae091432","tid":23920,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁驚訝做咩，菠蘿炒飯個菠蘿都係一樣"},{"pid":"7dbd84a70f215120e5db73d2d7c2e49e420308ad","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 刺身個帶子係急凍貨黎 個刺身帶子殻keep住回收再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁叫咩食會比較安全？<br />\n<br />\n利申：食過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n答唔到你<br />\n因為都幾多伏野下 例如啲蜆佢地長期唔理 賣得到就賣 好多時候好多隻蜆死左整臭哂個魚缸都唔理 直到老闆娘天神下凡睇店 老闆娘親自屌完一次先理 但就係理果一次就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係要講既就燒鮑魚 入面師父就真係睇住佢識動先拎出去 但死左唔動的話係掉翻佢入魚缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有海膽天婦羅好伏 一舊得一個中指指甲份量既海膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bc76e672008ced3c6401c9acaa9e06c8ad13a1","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地最近新翻生蠔 無錯今次真係原隻咁翻 要開殻 新鮮既個箱寫住日本直送有哂日期<br />\n但啲客食完又回收翻個殻 唔知係咪想用黎做燒蠔既殻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n始終廚房同前線人員關係都唔係咁好 之前尖沙咀總店有個日本師父係創業做到而家 on9到係唔比前線人員講野 一講野就指住你黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (佢而家掉左去分店)"},{"pid":"87c11f8c27f0da1ab96a4c12589945f3b8b62a9e","tid":23920,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022cf16265a508a7a6284d14426a54dfd931ecb1","tid":23920,"uid":5519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲背殼係咪再用 然後買現成肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，如果帶子殻 蠔殻 蟹殻都無燒過的話一律回收再用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心唔出奇<br />\n我做緊間酒店d殼都係洗完再用<br />\n一星期起碼用比人用過5次<br />\nN手系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}